    <text x="210" y="586" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12">End</text>
  </svg>
  </div>
  <p class="desc">
    The Teacher portal provides access to five core modules: Dashboard, Add Students, Records (Grade Entry), Attendance Management, Settings, and the AI Chatbot. The system guides the teacher through decision branches until the desired module is selected. If Logout is chosen, the session ends. Otherwise, the teacher returns to the navigation loop.
  </p>
  <div class="footer">Bachelor of Science in Information Technology</div>
</div>

